videos.headline: Reese makes difficult and-1 layup for Arizona
videos.description: Cate Reese gets the entry pass and navigates around a defender to draw the contact and make a difficult bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Reese makes difficult and-1 layup for Arizona) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald poses after splashing side-step 3
videos.description: Aari McDonald starts feeling it as she hits a side-step 3-pointer in transition and poses as UConn calls a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McDonald poses after splashing side-step 3) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers eclipses 100 points for the NCAA tournament
videos.description: Paige Bueckers pulls up to knock down a jumper to end a 7-0 Arizona run and notch 101 points in the tournament.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers eclipses 100 points for the NCAA tournament) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald splits defenders for and-1 bucket

videos.headline: Arizona celebrates its huge upset of UConn to advance to the title game
videos.description: Arizona celebrates as UConn misses the final shot to seal a 69-59 win to advance to the national championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Arizona celebrates its huge upset of UConn to advance to the title game) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arizona stuns UConn to advance to national championship
videos.description: Arizona pulls off the upset of UConn to make it an all-Pac-12 title game against Stanford.
